query: SELECT dusun from kartu_ibu_registration where userID='user12' group by dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun as desa, COUNT( kunjunganNeonatalpertama6sd48jamTanggaldanBulanKunjungan ) as KN1_laki_bulan_lalu FROM  kohort_bayi_neonatal_period INNER JOIN kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan ON kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.childId = kohort_bayi_neonatal_period.childid INNER JOIN kartu_anc_registration ON kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.motherid = kartu_anc_registration.motherid INNER JOIN kartu_ibu_registration ON kartu_anc_registration.kiid = kartu_ibu_registration.kiid WHERE kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kohort_bayi_neonatal_period.kunjunganNeonatalpertama6sd48jamTanggaldanBulanKunjungan !=  '-' AND kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.jeniskelamin =  'laki' AND kohort_bayi_neonatal_period.submissionDate BETWEEN  '2015-01-01' AND  '2015-11-31' GROUP BY kartu_ibu_registration.dusun
